fc: class Solution { public:     ListNode* mergeTwoLists(ListNode* l1, ListNode* l2) {         ListNode fake(0), *last = &fake;         while (l1 && l2) {             if (l1->val < l2->val) {                 last->next = l1;                 l1 = l1->next;             } else {                 last->next = l2;                 l2 = l2->next;             }             last = last->next;         }         last->next = l1 ? l1 : l2;         return fake.next;     } };

fc: class Solution { public:     vector<string> generateParenthesis(int n) {         vector<string> ans;         string cur(2 * n, '*');         backtrack(ans, cur, n, 0, 0);         return ans;     }  private:     void backtrack(vector<string> &ans, string &cur, int n, int l, int r) {         if (l >= n && r >= n) {             ans.push_back(cur);             return;         }         if (l < n) {             cur[l + r] = '(';             backtrack(ans, cur, n, l + 1, r);         }         if (r < l) {             cur[l + r] = ')';             backtrack(ans, cur, n, l, r + 1);         }     } };
